msItem.note:
The text also includes excerpts from Epistle to the Hebrews 4:14-5:6; First Epistle of Peter 2:5-6;
                           Gǝbra ḥawāryāt 20:15; an antiphon (kǝśtat) for the priests;
                           Wangel za-Mātewos 25:14-30; the prayer after the gospel and the prayer of the penance.

The text also includes excerpts from First Epistle to the Corinthians 15:23-39; First Epistle of Peter 3:15 - 4:11;
                           Gǝbra ḥawāryāt 7:55 - 8:2; an antiphon (kǝśtat) for the deacons;
                           Gospel of John 12:20-26; the prayer after the gospel and the prayer of the penance.

The text also includes excerpts from First Epistle to the Thessalonians 4:13-18; First Epistle of John 5:13-18;
                           Gǝbra ḥawāryāt 20:7-12; an antiphon (kǝśtat) for the children; Wangel za-Luqās
                           7:11-16; the prayer after the gospel.

The text includes excerpts from Epistle to the Hebrews 4:8-13 (the beginning and the end are changed);
                              Epistle of James 5:1-5; Gǝbra ḥawāryāt 17:23-28; Wangel za-Luqās
                              12:16-21.
